Privacy Policy for [Your Chrome Extension Name]

Effective Date: [Date]

This Privacy Policy explains how [Your Company Name] ("we," "us," or "our") collects, uses, discloses, and safeguards the information you provide when you use our Chrome extension [Your Chrome Extension Name] (the "Extension").

By using the Extension, you consent to the practices described in this Privacy Policy. If you do not agree to this Privacy Policy, please do not use the Extension.

Information We Collect

We do not collect any personal information or personally identifiable information through the Extension. However, we may collect non-personal information, such as browsing data or usage statistics, to improve the Extension's functionality and user experience.

How We Use Your Information

We may use non-personal information collected through the Extension for the following purposes:

To improve and enhance the functionality of the Extension.
To analyze trends and gather usage statistics.
To diagnose and resolve technical issues.
To customize the content and features of the Extension.
Disclosure of Your Information

We do not share, sell, or disclose your personal information to third parties. We may share non-personal, aggregated information with third-party service providers or partners for analysis and research purposes.

Data Security

We take reasonable measures to protect the information collected through the Extension from unauthorized access or disclosure. However, please be aware that no method of data transmission over the internet is entirely secure, and we cannot guarantee the security of your data.

Children's Privacy

The Extension is not intended for use by individuals under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you are a parent or guardian and believe that your child has provided us with personal information, please contact us, and we will delete that information.

Changes to this Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our data practices. We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any updates or changes.

Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please contact us at [Your Contact Email Address].